{{!
  PROFILE CUSTOM CONTENT SNIPPET

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom.hbs
  LOCATION: Inside the tab-content <div>, after any existing <div class="tab-pane"> entries

  INSTRUCTIONS:
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom.hbs
  2. Find the container <div> with class="tab-content"
  3. Copy the entire <div class="tab-pane fade"> block below (lines 24-26)
  4. Paste it inside the tab-content div, at the end of any existing tab-pane divs
  5. Save the file
  6. DO NOT change the id="inklings-tab-pane" - it matches the tab link from profile-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs

  ABOUT THE COMPONENT:
  The inklings-tab component is self-contained and handles everything:
  - Fetching Inklings
  - Creating new ones
  - Rolling dice
  - Submitting for staff review
  - Managing access (sharing, groups)

  It does NOT participate in the profile page's overall save flow - it saves changes immediately.

  IMPORTANT: The properties below (this.char, this.viewer, this.isStaff) must match
  what your profile-custom.hbs actually uses. These are common names but verify
  them against the rest of that template file.
}}

<div class="tab-pane fade" id="inklings-tab-pane">
  {{inklings-tab characterId=this.char.id viewerId=this.viewer.id isStaff=this.viewer.isStaff}}
</div>
